<T>__{cut to:}
<L>__{exterior street level plaza day}
<A>__{peter is still walking around on the street with the music playing. he crosses a large open windswept corporate plaza. as he approaches the building he sees sam rogers standing in front having a cigarette. he walks towards him and then finally decides to take off the headphones. the music stops and the wind kicks in.}
<C>__{peter}
<D>__{hello.}
